            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="mb-4">Secure Your Hotel with Professional Security Services</h2>
                <p class="mb-4">Get immediate hotel security deployment with our hospitality-focused protection services</p>
                <button class="btn btn-custom" aria-label="Request hotel security consultation" onclick="trackConsultationRequest()">Get a Free Security Assessment</button>
